text: Lypsimena strandiella is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1943. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Lypsimena strandiella. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1943
